 <p>Test passes if there is a filled green square and <strong>no red</strong>.</p><p>Test passes if there is a filled green square and <strong>no red</strong>.</p>
 <style>
.test {
    position: relative;
    width: 50px;
    height: 100px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: 25px solid black;
    border-image: filter(url(resources/green-transparent-200x200.png), drop-shadow(50px 0 0 green)) 75 / 18446744073709551691px / 50px;
}
.red {
    position: absolute;
    left: -25px;
    top: -25px;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: red;
    z-index: -1;
}
</style>
</body><body>
